Package org.owasp.dependencycheck.reporting

org.owasp.dependencycheck.reporting Contains classes used to generate reports.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ReportGenerator The ReportGenerator is used to, as the name implies, generate reports.
VelocityLoggerRedirect DependencyCheck uses Logger as a logging framework, and Apache Velocity uses a custom logging implementation that outputs to a file named velocity.log by default.
 

Enum Summary
ReportGenerator.Format An enumeration of the report formats.
